      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);font-size:17px;line-height:1.7;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto 40px;">Most mushroom products use mycelium grown on grain — which is mostly starch with minimal active compounds. We use <strong style="color:#fff;">100% fruiting body extracts</strong>, dual-extracted with hot water and alcohol to capture both water-soluble beta-glucans and fat-soluble triterpenes.</p>
